#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:0
msgid "# Roadmap指导"
msgstr "# Roadmap Guide"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:2
msgid "使用 GitHub Issue 来跟踪和管理各组织的计划及中长期目标。本文档为社区项目编写路线图类 Issue 提供参考和规范，以帮助创建和维护高质量的路线图。"
msgstr "Use GitHub Issues to track and manage the plans and medium-to-long-term goals of each organization. This document provides references and guidelines for writing roadmap-type Issues in community projects, helping to create and maintain high-quality roadmaps."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:4
msgid "下面是一个完整的路线图 Issue 示例，展示了所有推荐元素的实际应用。建议先查看此示例获得整体印象，再阅读后续的详细规范说明。"
msgstr "Below is a complete roadmap Issue example, demonstrating the practical application of all recommended elements. It is recommended to first review this example to get an overall impression, then read the subsequent detailed specification explanations."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:6
msgid ""
"```markdown\n"
"创建 Issue 标题：[Roadmap] Triton-Ascend Roadmap 2026 Q2\n"
"\n"
"---\n"
"# Triton-Ascend Roadmap 2026 Q2\n"
"\n"
"This quarter focuses on upstream Triton compatibility alignment, Ascend NPU backend performance optimization, and operator coverage expansion, continuously improving compiler stability and ecosystem integration capability.\n"
"\n"
"## Focus\n"
"\n"
"- Upstream Compatibility: Align with upstream Triton compiler frontend and IR changes, reduce fork divergence\n"
"- Backend Performance: Optimize Ascend NPU kernel generation and memory scheduling strategy\n"
"- Operator Coverage: Expand supported Triton ops and data types, improve end-to-end model coverage\n"
"- Usability: Improve debugging tools and error reporting for Ascend backend\n"
"\n"
"## Upstream Compatibility\n"
"\n"
"- [ ] **Triton 3.x IR and frontend alignment**\n"
"Goal: Align forked Triton frontend with upstream Triton 3.x IR changes, reduce merge conflict and divergence\n"
"Issue: [Related Issue link]\n"
"\n"
"- [ ] **Triton Language feature parity check**\n"
"Goal: Systematically check and supplement missing Triton language features (e.g., tl.dot with new dtypes, constexpr enhancements) on Ascend backend\n"
"Issue: [Related Issue link]\n"
"\n"
"## Backend Performance\n"
"\n"
"- [ ] **Ascend NPU kernel auto-tuning support**\n"
"Goal: Support Triton autotune mechanism on Ascend backend, enable dynamic kernel configuration selection\n"
"Owner: @contributor-a\n"
"Issue: [Related Issue link]\n"
"\n"
"- [ ] **Memory scheduling and L2 cache optimization**\n"
"Goal: Optimize memory allocation strategy and L2 cache utilization in generated Ascend kernels for large-scale training scenarios\n"
"Issue: [Related Issue link]\n"
"\n"
"## Operator Coverage\n"
"\n"
"- [ ] **FP8 dtype and mixed-precision ops support [🙋 Help Wanted]**\n"
"Goal: Support FP8 (E4M3/E5M2) dtype in tl.dot and related ops on Ascend backend, enabling FP8 training workflows\n"
"Owner: TBD\n"
"Issue: [Related Issue link]\n"
"\n"
"- [ ] **Additional Triton built-in ops support**\n"
"Goal: Add missing built-in ops (e.g., tl.cumsum, tl.reduce with custom axis, advanced indexing) on Ascend backend\n"
"Issue: [Related Issue link]\n"
"\n"
"## Usability\n"
"\n"
"- [ ] **Ascend backend debugging and error reporting improvement**\n"
"Goal: Improve Ascend backend error messages, add device-side debug print and kernel profiling support\n"
"Issue: [Related Issue link]\n"
"\n"
"## Sub-issues\n"
"\n"
"[Triton-Ascend Roadmap 2026 Q1 #xxx](link)\n"
"[FP8 Support Phase 2 #xxx](link)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:8
msgid "## 1. 标题格式"
msgstr "## 1. Title Format"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:10
msgid "**格式：** `[Roadmap] <Project Name> Roadmap <Time Range>`，季度发布使用 Q1/Q2/Q3/Q4 标记，半年度发布使用 H1/H2 标记"
msgstr "**Format:** `[Roadmap] <Project Name> Roadmap <Time Range>`, use Q1/Q2/Q3/Q4 for quarterly releases, and H1/H2 for semi-annual releases."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:12
msgid "**示例：**"
msgstr "**Example:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:14
msgid ""
"- `[Roadmap] Triton-Ascend Roadmap 2026 Q2`\n"
"- `[Roadmap] Triton-Ascend Roadmap 2026 H1`\n"
msgstr ""
"- `[Roadmap] Triton-Ascend Roadmap 2026 Q2`\n"
"- `[Roadmap] Triton-Ascend Roadmap 2026 H1`\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:16
msgid "## 2. 顶层内容"
msgstr "## 2. Top-Level Content"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:18
msgid "### 2.1 开篇描述（可选）"
msgstr "### 2.1 Opening Description (Optional)"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:20
msgid "提供项目概述、愿景或整体方向的简要总结。例如，简要描述 Triton-Ascend 本季度在上游对齐、后端性能和算子覆盖方面的目标。"
msgstr "Provide a brief summary of the project overview, vision, or overall direction. For example, briefly describe the goals of Triton-Ascend for this quarter in terms of upstream alignment, backend performance, and operator coverage."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:22
msgid "### 2.2 重点方向章节"
msgstr "### 2.2 Key Focus Areas Section"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:24
msgid "列出本周期最关键的 3-5 个重点方向，建议按项目的**功能领域**或**技术模块**分组，覆盖全局视角："
msgstr "List the 3-5 most critical focus areas for this cycle, recommended to be grouped by the project's **functional domains** or **technical modules**, covering a global perspective:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:26
msgid ""
"```markdown\n"
"## Focus\n"
"\n"
"• Upstream Compatibility: Align with upstream Triton compiler frontend and IR changes, reduce fork divergence\n"
"• Backend Performance: Optimize Ascend NPU kernel generation and memory scheduling strategy\n"
"• Operator Coverage: Expand supported Triton ops and data types, improve end-to-end model coverage\n"
"• Usability: Improve debugging tools and error reporting for Ascend backend\n"
"• Ecosystem Integration: Enhance integration with PyTorch, vLLM, and MindSpeed on Ascend backend\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:28
msgid "**特征：**"
msgstr "**Features:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:30
msgid "- 高层次概括和描述当前周期项目的主要开发方向，无需详细展开"
msgstr "- High-level summary and description of the main development directions for the current cycle project, without going into detailed specifics."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:32
msgid "## 3. 主要功能模块章节"
msgstr "## 3. Main Functional Modules Section"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:34
msgid "### 3.1 章节划分原则"
msgstr "### 3.1 Principles for Section Division"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:36
msgid "按项目的**功能领域**或**技术模块**分组，例如："
msgstr "Group by the project's **functional areas** or **technical modules**, for example:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:38
msgid ""
"- **Upstream Compatibility** - Upstream Triton frontend and IR alignment\n"
"- **Backend Performance** - Ascend NPU backend kernel generation and memory optimization\n"
"- **Operator Coverage** - Triton built-in ops and dtype support on Ascend\n"
"- **Usability** - Debugging tools and error reporting\n"
"- **Ecosystem Integration** - Integration with training/inference frameworks\n"
msgstr ""
"- **Upstream Compatibility** - Upstream Triton frontend and IR alignment\n"
"- **Backend Performance** - Ascend NPU backend kernel generation and memory optimization\n"
"- **Operator Coverage** - Triton built-in ops and dtype support on Ascend\n"
"- **Usability** - Debugging tools and error reporting\n"
"- **Ecosystem Integration** - Integration with training/inference frameworks\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:40
msgid "### 3.2 各模块结构"
msgstr "### 3.2 Module Structures"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:42
msgid "每个模块包含多个**具体工作项**，格式如下："
msgstr "Each module contains multiple **specific work items** in the following format:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:44
msgid ""
"```markdown\n"
"## [Module Name]\n"
"\n"
"- [ ] **Work item name/feature description**\n"
"Goal: [Goal description]\n"
"Owner: @GitHubID      [optional]\n"
"Issue: [Related Issue link]   [optional]\n"
"PR: [Related PR link]         [optional]\n"
"\n"
"- [ ] **Another work item**\n"
"Goal: [Goal description]\n"
"Owner: @GitHubID      [optional]\n"
"Issue: [Related Issue link]   [optional]\n"
"PR: [Related PR link]         [optional]\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:46
msgid "## 4. 关键元数据字段"
msgstr "## 4. Key Metadata Fields"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:48
msgid "每个工作项应包含以下关键信息："
msgstr "Each work item should contain the following key information:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:50
msgid "### 4.1 目标（Goal）"
msgstr "### 4.1 Goal"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:52
msgid ""
"- **含义**：工作目标或简要描述\n"
"- **用法**：说明该工作项的目标\n"
"- **示例**：`目标：在昇腾后端 tl.dot 中支持 FP8（E4M3/E5M2）数据类型`\n"
msgstr ""
"- **Meaning**: Work objective or brief description\n"
"- **Usage**: Describes the goal of the work item\n"
"- **Example**: `Goal: Support FP8 (E4M3/E5M2) data types in the Ascend backend tl.dot`\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:54
msgid "### 4.2 负责人（Owner）"
msgstr "### 4.2 Owner"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:56
msgid ""
"- **含义**：责任人\n"
"- **格式**：`负责人：@GitHubID`\n"
"- **用法**：明确谁负责或主导该工作项\n"
"- **示例**：`负责人：@contributor-a`\n"
msgstr ""
"- **Meaning**: Responsible person  \n"
"- **Format**: `负责人：@GitHubID`  \n"
"- **Usage**: Specify who is responsible for or leads the work item  \n"
"- **Example**: `负责人：@contributor-a`\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:58
msgid "### 4.3 Issue"
msgstr "### 4.3 Issue"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:60
msgid ""
"- **含义**：关联的 GitHub Issue\n"
"- **格式**：`Issue：<Issue 链接>`\n"
"- **用法**：跟踪详细设计和讨论\n"
"- **示例**：`Issue：https://github.com/triton-lang/triton-ascend/issues`\n"
msgstr ""
"- **Meaning**: Associated GitHub Issue\n"
"- **Format**: `Issue: <Issue link>`\n"
"- **Usage**: Track detailed design and discussion\n"
"- **Example**: `Issue: https://github.com/triton-lang/triton-ascend/issues`\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:62
msgid "### 4.4 PR（Pull Request）"
msgstr "### 4.4 PR (Pull Request)"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:64
msgid ""
"- **含义**：相关实现 PR\n"
"- **格式**：`PR：<PR 链接>`\n"
"- **用法**：关联实现工作\n"
"- **示例**：`PR：https://github.com/triton-lang/triton-ascend/pulls`\n"
msgstr ""
"- **Meaning**: Related implementation PR\n"
"- **Format**: `PR：<PR link>`\n"
"- **Usage**: Link to implementation work\n"
"- **Example**: `PR：https://github.com/triton-lang/triton-ascend/pulls`\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:66
msgid "## 5. 可选补充内容"
msgstr "## 5. Optional Supplementary Content"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:68
msgid "### 5.1 🙋 欢迎贡献标记"
msgstr "### 5.1 🙋 Welcome Contribution Mark"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:70
msgid "对于特别欢迎社区开发者贡献的工作项，建议使用 **[🙋 欢迎贡献]** 标记来标识："
msgstr "For work items that especially welcome contributions from community developers, it is recommended to use the **[🙋 Welcome Contributions]** label to identify them."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:72
msgid ""
"```markdown\n"
"- [ ] **FP8 dtype and mixed-precision ops support [🙋 Help Wanted]**\n"
"Goal: Support FP8 (E4M3/E5M2) dtype in tl.dot and related ops on Ascend backend\n"
"Owner: TBD\n"
"Issue: #123\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:74
msgid "### 5.2 子 Issue"
msgstr "### 5.2 Sub-Issue"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:76
msgid "在路线图 Issue 底部列出跨周期的相关路线图 Issue 或大工作项的分解 Issue。"
msgstr "List cross-cycle related roadmap Issues or decomposition Issues of large work items at the bottom of the roadmap Issue."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:78
msgid "**与工作项中 Issue 字段的区别：**"
msgstr "**Difference from the Issue field in work items:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:80
msgid ""
"- **工作项中的 Issue 字段**：链接到该工作项的具体设计、讨论或跟踪 Issue\n"
"- **子 Issue 章节**：用于关联其他周期的路线图 Issue（如上季度未完成的工作），或将大工作项分解为多个独立跟踪的子 Issue\n"
msgstr ""
"- **Issue Field in Work Item**: Links to the specific design, discussion, or tracking issue for that work item  \n"
"- **Sub-Issue Section**: Used to associate roadmap issues from other cycles (such as unfinished work from the previous quarter) or to break down large work items into multiple independently tracked sub-issues\n"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/community/roadmap_guide.md:82
msgid ""
"```markdown\n"
"## Sub-issues\n"
"\n"
"[Triton-Ascend Roadmap 2026 Q1 #xxx](link)  <!-- Related previous quarter Roadmap -->\n"
"[FP8 Support Phase 2 #xxx](link)            <!-- Breakdown of a large work item -->\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

